        {
            "__type__": "Note",
            "fields": [
                "IAM vs Identity Center Users",
                "IAM users are AWS local accounts, and don't scale well to other accounts / services. Identity Center users leverage org's IDP to provision access.<br><br><img src=\"paste-b099b4fd287ccc85e750fa5b96e5a982e9c8d743.jpg\">"
            ],
